"title": "4843: plague",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4843: plague",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Affliction with disease, destruction or environmental disaster as an expression of divine judgment, usually resulting in death. The purpose may be as a punishment or to encourage repentance.</p>\n<h2>The nature of plague</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:11-Ezek6:12\">EZK 6:11–6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:9\">2CH 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:12\">JER 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:8\">JER 27:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:21\">EZK 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:8\">REV 6:8</a></p>\n<h2>Plagues sent upon Egypt</h2>\n<h3>Plagues described</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:17-Exod7:18\">EXO 7:17–7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:5-Exod8:6\">EXO 8:5–8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:16-Exod8:17\">EXO 8:16–8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:21\">EXO 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:24\">EXO 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:6\">EXO 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:9-Exod9:10\">EXO 9:9–9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:22-Exod9:25\">EXO 9:22–9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:4-Exod10:6\">EXO 10:4–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:13-Exod10:15\">EXO 10:13–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:21-Exod10:23\">EXO 10:21–10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:4-Exod11:6\">EXO 11:4–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29-Exod12:30\">EXO 12:29–12:30</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues withdrawn in answer to prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:12-Exod8:13\">EXO 8:12–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:29\">EXO 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:29\">EXO 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:33\">EXO 9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:18-Exod10:19\">EXO 10:18–10:19</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues recalled and celebrated</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:41-Ps78:51\">PSA 78:41–78:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:26-Ps105:36\">PSA 105:26–105:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:8-Ps135:9\">PSA 135:8–135:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:10\">AMO 4:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:36\">ACT 7:36</a></p>\n<h2>Plagues sent upon Israel</h2>\n<h3>Plagues threatened for breaking God's covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:23-Lev26:26\">LEV 26:23–26:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:16\">LEV 26:14–26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:20-Deut28:24\">DEU 28:20–28:24</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues experienced in fulfilment of God's covenant</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:33-Exod32:35\">EXO 32:33–32:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:31-Num11:34\">NUM 11:31–11:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:36-Num14:38\">NUM 14:36–14:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:41-Num16:50\">NUM 16:41–16:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:3-Num25:9\">NUM 25:3–25:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:11-2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:11–24:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:9-1Chr21:17\">1CH 21:9–21:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:2-Joel1:12\">JOL 1:2–1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:6-Amos4:11\">AMO 4:6–4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues withdrawn after intercession or obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:10-Num14:20\">NUM 14:10–14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:46-Num16:48\">NUM 16:46–16:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:6-Num21:9\">NUM 21:6–21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:6-Num25:11\">NUM 25:6–25:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:18-2Sam24:25\">2SA 24:18–24:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:18-1Chr21:26\">1CH 21:18–21:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:37-1Kgs8:40\">1KI 8:37–8:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:28-2Chr6:31\">2CH 6:28–6:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:23\">PSA 106:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:28-Ps106:31\">PSA 106:28–106:31</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues announced by prophets as God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:5-Jer21:10\">JER 21:5–21:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:10\">JER 24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:17-Jer29:19\">JER 29:17–29:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:17\">JER 34:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:13\">JER 44:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:12\">EZK 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:17\">EZK 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:27\">EZK 33:27</a></p>\n<h2>Plagues sent upon other nations</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6-1Sam5:12\">1SA 5:6–5:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:22\">ISA 19:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:8\">JER 28:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:22-Ezek28:23\">EZK 28:22–28:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:5-Hab3:6\">HAB 3:5–3:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:12-Zech14:15\">ZEC 14:12–14:15</a></p>\n<h2>Apocalyptic visions of plague as God's judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:11\">LUK 21:11</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7\">MAT 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:8\">MRK 13:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:8\">REV 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:6\">REV 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:1\">REV 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:6-Rev15:8\">REV 15:6–15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:1-Rev16:21\">REV 16:1–16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:4-Rev18:8\">REV 18:4–18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:18\">REV 22:18</a></p>\n<h2>Divine protection from plague</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:3-Ps91:8\">PSA 91:3–91:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:22-Exod8:23\">EXO 8:22–8:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:4\">EXO 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:6\">EXO 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:26\">EXO 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:23\">EXO 10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:7\">EXO 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:13\">EXO 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:23\">EXO 12:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:27\">EXO 12:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:9\">2CH 20:9</a></p>",
